 />汤姆·史密斯</p><p>今年的《 Splendor Festival》将在整个周末看到一个全新的舞台，这将使他们的白天迪斯科舞会由<em>值班之</em>星Vicky McClure和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/reverend-and-the-makers">Reverend＆The Makers</a>的Jon McClure策划。这还将以电子音乐节目的尚未浏览的阵容来结束这两天。</p><p> “ Splendor已成为家庭和经验丰富的演出者的杰出周末，也是它带给该地区的文化和经济价值的重要事件。我们很高兴终于回来了另一个出色的阵容，现在分散了两天和六个截然不同的阶段，为每个人与我们一起享受周末的巨大价值。” 。</p><p>辉煌的回归还将为当地经济带来欢迎，因为它吸引了成千上万的游客在周末前往城市。今年，组织者正在建立周末节日的吸引力，并在节日旁边引入了一个住宿合作伙伴。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DES6y9AsLoX/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.88